      <title>私人信贷为贝恩资本收购 PowerSchool 提供债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/private-credit-provides-debt-for-bain-s-powerschool-buyout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群私人信贷机构为贝恩资本以 56 亿美元收购 PowerSchool Holdings Inc. 提供了债务融资，击败了同样参与融资的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/private-credit-provides-debt-for-bain-s-powerschool-buyout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:49:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债务市场推动“先买后付”消费模式复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/debt-markets-are-fueling-buy-now-pay-later-s-resurgence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPal Holdings Inc. 和 Klarna Bank AB 等提供先买后付服务的公司正在出售由消费者贷款支持的债务，因为他们找到了在高利率环境下为其业务融资的新方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/debt-markets-are-fueling-buy-now-pay-later-s-resurgence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据令美联储降息预期减弱，美国国债收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/treasuries-yields-surge-as-hot-jobs-data-dim-fed-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场意外走强，迫使交易员减少对美联储今年降息的押注，美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/treasuries-yields-surge-as-hot-jobs-data-dim-fed-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:39:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登就援助延迟向泽连斯基道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/biden-apologizes-to-zelenskiy-for-delay-in-aid-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登向乌克兰总统泽连斯基道歉，因为 2.25 亿美元援助计划的批准被推迟。拜登告诉泽连斯基：“我不会抛弃你。我们仍然会全力以赴。”他们在巴黎会面。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/biden-apologizes-to-zelenskiy-for-delay-in-aid-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:34:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利法院维持对 ION 子公司股息融资的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/italian-restriction-on-how-ion-raises-debt-for-dividends-upheld-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利一家法院支持政府的一项决定，限制 ION 集团旗下子公司如何使用债券销售收益，可能禁止其通过举债向母公司支付股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/italian-restriction-on-how-ion-raises-debt-for-dividends-upheld-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
